channel.title: What is this error on runserver?
channel.description:
It occurs half the time, whenever I start the server. Sometimes I have to keep restarting the server until it lets me log in because it says Error Connecting To Server, but everyone else gets in fine.
Yes I AM the host, and the owner. Sometimes it even says i'm already logged in, and i'm not, it gives everyone else that too.
Whats wrong?
